00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.800 align:middle line:84%
>> The US military confirms
the first interstellar object

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:09.510 align:middle line:84%
to hit Earth was years before
Oumuamua and corroborates

00:00:09.510 --> 00:00:13.020 align:middle line:84%
research done by a
famous astronomer.

00:00:13.020 --> 00:00:15.860 align:middle line:90%
